Just for posterity, I was able to resolve the issue by doing the following:

{code:javascript}
...
/* Make sure the DB file is removed first */
var db = Ti.Database.open(DB_NAME).remove();
/* Don't forget to close the removed database... */
db.close();
...
{code}
